Welcome to AEJuice Pack Manager API

Contact jacob@aejuice.com for any questions or recommendations.

### Requirements

- Install After Effects CC15 or higher
- Install Pack Manager

AEJuice products are managed by our plugin Pack Manager. 

**Windows**: https://aejuice.com/pack_manager/AEJuice_Pack_Manager.zip

**macOS**: https://aejuice.com/pack_manager/AEJuice_Pack_Manager_mac.zip

Log in if you need to access paid product (Account-Log in).

### Integration

Add the following line to your code:

```javascript
// Initialize Pack Manager
eval("@JSXBIN@ES@2.0@");
```

### API Methods

All API calls can be made through the standardized `PackManager.run` method:

```javascript
PackManager.run(className, settings);
```

Where:
- `className`: String identifying the class
- `settings`: Configuration object for the specific action


Example usage:
```javascript
var file = PackManager.run("Voiceover", {
    text: "Your text to convert to speech",
    lang: "en-US",
    voice: "AIGenerate1"
});
```

`text` - text for voiceover
`lang` - language same as appears in Pack Manager Voiceover AI
`voice` - voice name same as appears in Pack Manager Voiceover AI

@returns File|null - generated file or null if generation has failed

Script can throw an error if you run out of available minutes.
